{"tid":6120,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉載求唱）再奶多一次 再舔多幾次","createTime":"2016-11-27T07:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T14:56:37.000Z","uid":3661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe65e6c112284cdafed6c99ee9b3a7a70a963d29","tid":6120,"uid":3661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"［轉載］<br />\n腳　抱著那美腿來舔摸 <br />\n看　白褲裡晃然清楚 <br />\n誰及倆鳩猥瑣　淫辱吹拂鮑邊的野草 <br />\n<br />\n拍　拍著看青頭撫摸 <br />\n太　太快樂卻無視起底結果<br />\n來襲對波飄晃　還後悔碌鳩扯起未爆房 <br />\n<br />\n再奶多一次　再舔多幾次 <br />\n再可不可以回到輕吻閪邊的那點 <br />\n其實我不只這需要<br />\n碌鳩會旋轉　飄往除鞋屌腳的那年 <br />\nJ多兩次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那　那合照三人對望 <br />\n這　這公廁迷倒香港 <br />\n而為你寫的歌　 <br />\n如未了　約定一生一世還在播<br />\n<br />\n再奶多一次　再舔多幾次 <br />\n再可不可以回到輕吻閪邊的那點 <br />\n其實你只是個公廁 <br />\n碌鳩會旋轉 雙腿環游舔 <br />\n竟不怎為意 對面偷影的那片<br />\n最後都upload上線 <br />\n<br />\n再玩多一次　再舐多一次 <br />\n再可不可以回到輕吻閪邊興奮點 <br />\n遺憾嘴角總停不了 <br />\n多一秒留戀　差一秒射精改寫意義 <br />\n回憶的腳　想著舐多一次　只求舐多次<br />\n<br />\n由高登轉載過黎，等左好耐都冇人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打出手唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1b44d6f8b198cdcbd117f44d9022e1087b40ea","tid":6120,"uid":27351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e5be5fb86c067cdb9c102d6dad306a1ac694f0","tid":6120,"uid":3661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n風箏"},{"pid":"e5298188215fd0e9d2489aa6325f860ca39deb42","tid":6120,"uid":1195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/